valinta__suomifi-tunnistaminen-roadmap: Suomi.fi e-Identification is a shared identification service for public administration e-services. It will make identification secure and easy. You can use the identification method of your preference.
valinta__toisten_maiden_tunnistautumista: Use the identification service of an other EU Member State
valinta__vaihtoehto__otsikko_valitse_maa: Select country in the common European identification scheme (eIDAS)
valinta__palaa_tunnistajan_valintaan: Go back to method of identification
